<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>My Applications - JobBoard</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 20px; max-width: 900px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
        #tracking-page { }
        #applications-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 20px; }
        #applications-table th, #applications-table td { border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 10px; text-align: left; }
        #applications-table th { background-color: #f0f0f0; }
        #status-filter { margin-top: 10px; padding: 6px; font-size: 1em; }
        button { padding: 6px 12px; font-size: 0.9em; cursor: pointer; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="tracking-page">
        <h1>My Applications</h1>

        <form method="get" action="{{ url_for('tracking.my_applications') }}">
            <label for="status-filter">Filter by Status:</label>
            <select id="status-filter" name="status" onchange="this.form.submit()">
                <option value="All" {% if status_filter == 'All' %}selected{% endif %}>All</option>
                <option value="Under Review" {% if status_filter == 'Under Review' %}selected{% endif %}>Under Review</option>
                <option value="Interview" {% if status_filter == 'Interview' %}selected{% endif %}>Interview</option>
                <option value="Rejected" {% if status_filter == 'Rejected' %}selected{% endif %}>Rejected</option>
            </select>
        </form>

        {% if applications %}
        <table id="applications-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Job Title</th>
                    <th>Company</th>
                    <th>Status</th>
                    <th>Applied Date</th>
                    <th>Action</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {% for app in applications %}
                <tr>
                    <td>{{ app.job_title }}</td>
                    <td>{{ app.company_name }}</td>
                    <td>{{ app.status }}</td>
                    <td>{{ app.applied_date }}</td>
                    <td>
                        <button id="view-application-button-{{ app.application_id }}" onclick="location.href='{{ url_for('tracking.application_detail', application_id=app.application_id) }}'">View</button>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                {% endfor %}
            </tbody>
        </table>
        {% else %}
            <p>No applications found.</p>
        {% endif %}
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

companies.html
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Companies Directory - JobBoard</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 20px; max-width: 900px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
        #companies-page { }
        #search-company-input { padding: 8px; width: 300px; font-size: 1em; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .company-card { border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; border-radius: 5px; }
        .company-name { font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2em; }
        .industry, .location, .employee-count { color: #555; margin-top: 5px; }
        button { margin-top: 10px; padding: 7px 12px; font-size: 0.9em; cursor: pointer; }
        #back-to-dashboard { margin-top: 20px; padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 1em; cursor: pointer; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="companies-page">
        <h1>Companies Directory</h1>

        <form method="get" action="{{ url_for('companies.companies_directory') }}">
            <input id="search-company-input" name="search" type="text" placeholder="Search companies by name or industry" value="{{ request.args.get('search', '') }}" />
            <button type="submit">Search</button>
        </form>

        {% if companies %}
            {% for company in companies %}
            <div class="company-card">
                <div class="company-name">{{ company.company_name }}</div>
                <div class="industry">Industry: {{ company.industry }}</div>
                <div class="location">Location: {{ company.location }}</div>
                <div class="employee-count">Employees: {{ company.employee_count }}</div>
                <button id="view-company-button-{{ company.company_id }}" onclick="location.href='{{ url_for('companies.company_profile', company_id=company.company_id) }}'">View Profile</button>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        {% else %}
            <p>No companies found.</p>
        {% endif %}

        <button id="back-to-dashboard" onclick="location.href='{{ url_for('dashboard.dashboard') }}'">Back to Dashboard</button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

company_profile.html
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>{{ company.company_name }} - Profile - JobBoard</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 20px; max-width: 900px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
        #company-profile-page { }
        #company-info { border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        h1 { margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .company-detail { margin-top: 10px; }
        #company-jobs { }
        .job-card { border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; border-radius: 5px; }
        .job-title { font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.1em; }
        button { margin-top: 10px; padding: 7px 12px; font-size: 0.9em; cursor: pointer; }
        #back-to-companies { margin-top: 20px; padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 1em; cursor: pointer; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="company-profile-page">
        <div id="company-info">
            <h1 id="company-name">{{ company.company_name }}</h1>
            <div class="company-detail"><strong>Industry:</strong> {{ company.industry }}</div>
            <div class="company-detail"><strong>Location:</strong> {{ company.location }}</div>
            <div class="company-detail"><strong>Employees:</strong> {{ company.employee_count }}</div>
            <div class="company-detail" style="margin-top: 15px;">{{ company.description }}</div>
        </div>

        <div id="company-jobs">
            <h2>Jobs at {{ company.company_name }}</h2>
            {% if jobs %}
                {% for job in jobs %}
                <div class="job-card">
                    <div class="job-title">{{ job.title }}</div>
                    <button id="view-job-button-{{ job.job_id }}" onclick="location.href='{{ url_for('job_details.job_details', job_id=job.job_id) }}'">View Job</button>
                </div>
                {% endfor %}
            {% else %}
                <p>No jobs available for this company.</p>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        <button id="back-to-companies" onclick="location.href='{{ url_for('companies.companies_directory') }}'">Back to Companies Directory</button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

resumes.html
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>My Resumes - JobBoard</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 20px; max-width: 700px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
        #resume-page { }
        #resumes-list { margin-top: 20px; }
        .resume-item { border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; border-radius: 5px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        .resume-info { }
        .resume-filename { font-weight: bold; }
        .resume-date { color: #555; margin-top: 5px; }
        button { padding: 6px 12px; font-size: 0.9em; cursor: pointer; }
        #upload-resume-form { margin-top: 30px; }
        input[type="file"] { margin-top: 10px; }
        #upload-resume-button { margin-top: 10px; padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 1em; cursor: pointer; }
        #back-to-dashboard { margin-top: 30px; padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 1em; cursor: pointer; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="resume-page">
        <h1>My Resumes</h1>

        {% with messages = get_flashed_messages() %}
          {% if messages %}
            <ul style="color: green;">
              {% for message in messages %}
                <li>{{ message }}</li>
              {% endfor %}
            </ul>
          {% endif %}
        {% endwith %}

        <div id="resumes-list">
            {% if resumes %}
                {% for resume in resumes %}
                <div class="resume-item">
                    <div class="resume-info">
                        <div class="resume-filename">{{ resume.filename }}</div>
                        <div class="resume-date">Uploaded: {{ resume.upload_date }}</div>
                    </div>
                    <form method="post" action="{{ url_for('resumes.delete_resume', resume_id=resume.resume_id) }}" onsubmit="return confirm('Are you sure you want to delete this resume?');">
                        <button id="delete-resume-button-{{ resume.resume_id }}" type="submit">Delete</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
                {% endfor %}
            {% else %}
                <p>No resumes uploaded yet.</p>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div id="upload-resume-form">
            <form method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" action="{{ url_for('resumes.upload_resume') }}">
                <label for="resume-upload">Upload New Resume (pdf, doc, docx, txt):</label>
                <input id="resume-upload" name="resume-upload" type="file" accept=".pdf,.doc,.docx,.txt" required />
                <button id="upload-resume-button" type="submit">Upload Resume</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <button id="back-to-dashboard" onclick="location.href='{{ url_for('dashboard.dashboard') }}'">Back to Dashboard</button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

search_results.html
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Search Results - JobBoard</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 20px; max-width: 900px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
        #search-results-page { }
        #search-query-display { font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        #results-tabs { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .tab-button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-bottom: none;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin-right: 5px;
            font-weight: normal;
        }
        .tab-button.active {
            background-color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-top: 2px solid #007BFF;
        }
        #search-jobs, #search-companies { border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; }
        .job-card, .company-card {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .job-title, .company-name { font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.1em; }
        .company-industry, .job-location { color: #555; margin-top: 5px; }
        button { margin-top: 10px; padding: 7px 12px; font-size: 0.9em; cursor: pointer; }
        #no-results-message { color: #777; font-style: italic; }
    </style>
    <script>
        function switchTab(tabName) {
            document.getElementById('search-jobs').style.display = (tabName === 'jobs') ? 'block' : 'none';
            document.getElementById('search-companies').style.display = (tabName === 'companies') ? 'block' : 'none';

            document.getElementById('tab-jobs').classList.toggle('active', tabName === 'jobs');
            document.getElementById('tab-companies').classList.toggle('active', tabName === 'companies');
        }
        window.onload = function() {
            switchTab('{{ tab }}');
        };
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="search-results-page">
        <h1>Search Results</h1>
        <div id="search-query-display">Search Query: "{{ search_query }}"</div>

        <div id="results-tabs">
            <button id="tab-jobs" class="tab-button" onclick="switchTab('jobs')">Jobs</button>
            <button id="tab-companies" class="tab-button" onclick="switchTab('companies')">Companies</button>
        </div>

        <div id="search-jobs">
            {% if job_results %}
                {% for job in job_results %}
                <div class="job-card">
                    <div class="job-title">{{ job.title }}</div>
                    <div class="company-name">{{ job.company_name }}</div>
                    <div class="job-location">{{ job.location }}</div>
                    <button onclick="location.href='{{ url_for('job_details.job_details', job_id=job.job_id) }}'">View Job</button>
                </div>
                {% endfor %}
            {% else %}
                <div id="no-results-message">No job results found.</div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div id="search-companies" style="display:none;">
            {% if company_results %}
                {% for company in company_results %}
                <div class="company-card">
                    <div class="company-name">{{ company.company_name }}</div>
                    <div class="company-industry">Industry: {{ company.industry }}</div>
                    <div class="company-location">Location: {{ company.location }}</div>
                    <button onclick="location.href='{{ url_for('companies.company_profile', company_id=company.company_id) }}'">View Profile</button>
                </div>
                {% endfor %}
            {% else %}
                <div id="no-results-message">No company results found.</div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```
