### 4) Summary of file names and corresponding functionalities:

| File Name           | Functionality Summary                                                                                   |
|---------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| `main.py`           | Main entry point; registers blueprints; runs Flask app on port 5000.                                   |
