| `routes/listings.py` | Defines job listings blueprint; supports filtering and searching jobs; renders listings page.          |
| `routes/job_details.py` | Defines job details blueprint; shows detailed job info; supports apply now redirect.                  |
| `routes/application_form.py` | Handles job application form submission; validates inputs; saves resumes and applications.         |
| `routes/tracking.py` | Tracks submitted applications; supports filtering by status; renders tracking page.                    |
| `routes/companies.py` | Lists companies; supports search; shows company profiles and jobs.                                    |
| `routes/resumes.py`  | Manages resume uploads, listing, and deletion.                                                         |
| `routes/search_results.py` | Handles search results for jobs and companies; supports tab switching between results.              |
| `validators.py`      | Contains validation functions for emails, required fields, file types, and filename sanitization.      |
| `tests/test_dashboard.py` | Contains unit tests for dashboard page accessibility, element presence, and navigation button redirects.|

